    mc "当然，斯潘夫人。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrudemicha16.rpy:155
translate chinese gertrudemicha16_a9c38559:

    # sc "Okay, we should get cleaned up. People are going to notice that you're gone."
    sc "好了，我们该去清理一下了。大家会发现你不在的。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrudemicha16.rpy:156
translate chinese gertrudemicha16_15a18643:

    # sc "And [pcname], you better get to class. This session has gone on a little longer than most."
    sc "还有[pcname]，你最好去上课。这次的课程比平时要长一点。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrudemicha16.rpy:159
translate chinese gertrudemicha16_d1e3a423:

    # sc "But this was a lot of fun. I haven't been with another woman in a long time."
    sc "不过这真的很有趣。我好久没和别的女人在一起了。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrudemicha16.rpy:160
translate chinese gertrudemicha16_a3feaaf8:

    # sc "You've both made me feel really good today."
    sc "今天你们俩都让我感觉特别好。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrudemicha16.rpy:161
translate chinese gertrudemicha16_dc58c25e:

    # mc "I'm glad, Mrs. Spann."
    mc "我很高兴，斯潘夫人。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrudemicha16.rpy:162
translate chinese gertrudemicha16_117f39b6:

    # sc "Okay, get cleaned up and dressed. Let's go."
    sc "好了，去洗漱穿好衣服。我们走吧。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrudemicha16.rpy:165
translate chinese gertrudemicha16_4626218c:

    # "I don't have a lot of time before class starts, so I quickly get dressed and tell them goodbye and then head to class."
    "离上课没多少时间了，所以我赶紧穿好衣服，跟她们道别，然后赶去上课。"

# game/Scenes/Gertrude/gertrudemicha16.rpy:166
translate chinese gertrudemicha16_5bac5e5d:

    # "But I'll be thinking about that counseling session for a long time."
    "但我会很长一段时间都在回想那次咨询。"

